to the physical world

57:02.600 --> 57:05.311
and gives you some influence
over its actions."

57:06.228 --> 57:08.189
Totems?

57:21.619 --> 57:23.771
<i>Their system's been on "away"
for a week straight.</i>

57:23.871 --> 57:28.667
<i>Their garage hasn't been opened either,
and the grocery-delivery service is on hold.</i>

57:38.594 --> 57:41.555
Guess they decided to mourn
